"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1934563-alexander-zverev-complains-olympics-2024-tennis\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Alexander Zverevhas hit out at theOlympic Gameschiefs after the tennis ace 'suffered' with the conditions of the athlete's village in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.997923712398967, \"rank\": 0.0015008578161143408, \"text\": \"Alexander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\"}, {\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999795045371, \"rank\": 2.0495382517461588e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Defending Olympic champion Zverev reached the quarter-final stage in the French capital, but was dumped out of the singles competition by Lorenzo Musetti.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9992694500766982, \"rank\": 0.0006089125248210075, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It probably would not have counted for much, givenNovak Djokovicappeared to be on a one-man mission to take home gold.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, in the wake of last week's Olympic tennis meet, Zverev has blasted the organisers of the Games.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Speaking to the Tennis Channel, Zverev said: \\\"I preferred Tokyo because I prefer to win gold, of course, but it's always special to be in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_Channel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tennis Channel\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_Channel\"}, {\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.984961823747289, \"rank\": 0.010663118994852297, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This year it was strange because it was in Roland Garros, a place we all know very well.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999984877863491, \"rank\": 1.5118539018049964e-06, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at the same time, it was very different.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Village wasn't the best, I have to say.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed there, the whole German team stayed there, our federation wanted it.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9952631964710611, \"rank\": 0.004683317946865135, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We suffered a little because of food, we suffered a little from sleeping conditions.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was no air conditioning in the rooms either, which was a bit difficult for me but it was the same for everyone so I do not complain.\\\"\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The lack of air conditioning was picked up on by the Team GB chiefs in the build-up to the Games, with the rooms housing British athletes having been retro-fitted with AC units.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9865940687647077, \"rank\": 0.012309600118188624, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998129983215706, \"rank\": 0.00015115579030147277, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9809494016785003, \"rank\": 0.015147154192417462, \"text\": \"AC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zverev and his German counterparts were not so lucky.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9952631964710611, \"rank\": 0.004683317946865135, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Something the ATP world No.4 wasn't too pleased about: \\\"Because of that, I think Tokyo was much better and the organisation was also much better.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_Tennis_Professionals\", \"score\": 0.9984901822072659, \"rank\": 0.0015120843562262238, \"text\": \"ATP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_Tennis_Professionals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_Tennis_Professionals\"}, {\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.984961823747289, \"rank\": 0.010663118994852297, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nevertheless, it was a great experience to be there with all the athletes and it was nice to be back in the Olympic village.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the win is always the most fun part and this time I did not get it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The German will be keen to get Paris out of his mind, given the US Open is just two weeks away.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9952631964710611, \"rank\": 0.004683317946865135, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999795045371, \"rank\": 2.0495382517461588e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zverev is yet to win a Grand Slam, having last come close at the French Open earlier in the summer.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The 27-year-old was brushed aside in the final byCarlos Alcaraz, with Zverev admitting he's still hurting from the defeat: \\\"We are both physically strong but he's a beast, he's an animal for sure and the intensity that he plays tennis is different to that of other people.\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.742501809072213e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He can do so many different things.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He changed his tactic a lot in the fifth set.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I had to play a lot higher, a lot deeper for me to not create as much power, especially with the shadows on the court.\\\"\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.713480715639042e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.713480715639042e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"